stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_load: load BLOB_SCHEDULE from CL config
    q_load --> q_iter: for entry in BLOB_SCHEDULE
    q_iter --> q_check: compare current_epoch with entry.EPOCH
    q_check --> q_update: current_epoch >= entry.EPOCH
    q_check --> q_iter: current_epoch < entry.EPOCH
    q_update --> q_iter: MAX_BLOBS_PER_BLOCK = entry.MAX_BLOBS_PER_BLOCK
    q_iter --> [*]: return resolved MAX_BLOBS_PER_BLOCK
